<paragraph id="B8D4A47071C67B1EE37CCA179AB5B421" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="93DA1041FB96CAD472961CB6EEEF8513" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
MEXICO. Jalisco, La Huerta, Est. Biologia, Chamela, 
<emphasis id="8D7A04ECC150B7EA997095B3D5510576" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">E. Lott, J.A. Solis &amp; S.H. Bullock</emphasis>
